[SN]TITLE[SN]
Woman 'critical' after being hit by car in Aberystwyth

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A woman is in a critical condition after being hit by a car in Ceredigion.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Dyfed-Powys Police said the incident happened near the Starling Cloud pub on Boulevard St Brieuc in Aberystwyth just before 18:30 GMT on Monday.
The woman suffered serious injuries and was airlifted to University Hospital of Wales in Cardiff.
Anyone who witnessed the incident involving a white Toyota Yaris has been asked to contact police on 101.
